<div class="p-demo__sections">
  <section class="p-demo__section" id="place-embed">
    <h2 class="p-demo__heading">Place 埋め込み（1地点）</h2>
    <p>
      ピンが<strong>1地点だけ</strong>のとき。
    </p>
    <div class="p-demo__map">
      <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3241.7479757770916!2d139.74285797578673!3d35.658580472594515!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x60188bbd9009ec09%3A0x481a93f0d2a409dd!2z5p2x5Lqs44K_44Ov44O8!5e0!3m2!1sja!2sjp!4v1779497398947!5m2!1sja!2sjp" width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
